title: CPU Speed Professional  [akhiugo]
description:
If you've ever wondered exactly how fast your CPU is running, this great little application will tell you.

Simply click the 'Test CPU Speed' button and see CPU Speed Professional go to work. 

CPU Speed Professional records processor speeds from all over the world.

You can check your speed score in the worldwide ranking tables.

Yes it's simple. Yes it's free. Enjoy!
